"JET SKIMMER" HOVERCRAFT
Sponsored by the Port of Oakland, SFO Helicopter Airlines
Inc., Bell Aerosystems Co., and the Federal Housing and Home
Finance Agency, the world's first commercial Hovercraft Air
Cushion Vehicle test is being conducted on San Francisco Bay.
The "Jet Skimmer" Hovercraft operated by SFO skims a few
feet above the ground or water supported by a cushion of air
forced downward by ducted fans. It is capable of a maximum
speed of 70 knots and has a seating capacity of 15.
The "Jet Skimmer" Hovercraft travels between the Oakland
International Airport and downtown San Francisco and the San
Francisco International Airport.

SAN FRANCISCO & OAKLAND HELICOPTER AIRLINES INC.
Metropolitan Oakland International Airport
P.O. Box 2525, Oakland, California 94614
Phone: LO 9-1111
CREDIT CARDS-SFO Helicopter Airlines honors the American
Express, BankAmericard, Diner's, Universal Air Travel Plan and
the SFO Helicopter Airlines credit cards.
EXCURSION FARE—A special same-day round trip excursion
fare via any scheduled flight is available for only $6.00 plus tax.
Advance reservations are not permitted under this fare. You get
a sightseeing trip with a panoramic view of the beautiful San
Francisco bay area. It's great for taking photographs!
FAMILY PLAN — SFO Helicopter Airlines Family Plan is available
via any flight from 12:00 Noon Monday through 6:00 a.m.
Friday. The head of the family pays one full fare, the spouse
and/or children 12 through 21 years of age accompanying the
head of the family on the same flight travel for each 75% of
the full adult one way fare.
GROUP FARES — Special group fares for 10 or more persons are
available via any regularly scheduled flights between most points
on the SFO Helicopter Airlines system. Two children between
2 and 12 years of age will be considered as one person in deter-
mining the size of the group.
MILITARY FARES — Military personnel on furlough or leave trav-
eling at their own expense in uniform and in possession of
authorized military leave papers travel for each 50% of the full
adult one way fare.
